TBT: To making the first-ever pink glass Tyrannosaurus trophy @cleinstituteart Making pieces in this style has opened up a whole new realm of possibilities in my work and I’m excited to share this and some really cool things I’ve been working on with my students this summer @theglassfurnace outside Istanbul! This is by far my favorite place to teach and worth every penny. Truly an awesome adventure. Hope to see you there! September 9-20th. Follow the link in my bio to signup.
